pve-center (1.0.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * O6: i18n translations moved from inline Python dicts to external JSON files (one per language).
  * Only the active language is loaded into memory instead of all five.
  * Translators can now edit a single JSON file without touching Python.

 -- Taurus McLure <taurus@mclure.ru>  Fri, 19 Jun 2026 12:40:00 +0300

pve-center (1.0.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * O1: debounced tree rebuild — intermediate updates (final=False) coalesce via 150ms QTimer instead of N full rebuilds.
  * Selection and scroll position preserved across tree rebuilds.

 -- Taurus McLure <taurus@mclure.ru>  Fri, 19 Jun 2026 00:30:00 +0300

pve-center (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Code audit fixes: executor.map workers (snapshots/disks), ClusterTasksWorker leak, freeze detector logging.
  * i18n: 22 hardcoded Russian strings wrapped in tr(), translations added for 5 languages.
  * Performance: O(1) dict lookup for nodes_cfg and all_vms (was O(N) linear scan, ~31+7 sites).
  * QTreeWidgetItemIterator replaces recursion in update_node_statuses.
  * Filter tables: debounce 200ms + lower-case cache + blockSignals.
  * Table factory: _make_table consolidates 13 QTableWidget boilerplate blocks.
  * Storage type explicit in ITEM_KEY_ROLE (was heuristic by dots/slashes).
  * Column width fix: datacenter_summary reset resize modes before reconfigure.
  * Removed dead watchdog timer, os.chdir side-effect, dead code comments.

 -- Taurus McLure <taurus@mclure.ru>  Thu, 18 Jun 2026 22:00:00 +0300

